{
  "version": "1.0",
  "title": "最後一盞燈",
  "silence_ms": 500,
  "output_format": "flac",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "chinese_story.txt",
    "created": "2026-04-06T15:31:42",
    "author": "",
    "language": "zh"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "seg_1",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "那是一九四九年的冬天，上海的街道像一條冰封的河。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "storytelling",
      "speed": 0.97
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_2",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "林書瑤站在外灘的石欄邊，望著黃浦江上漂流的碎冰。她的手裡握著一封信——那封她讀了三十七遍、卻始終無法回覆的信。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.88
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_3",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "信是陳懷遠寄來的。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "storytelling",
      "speed": 0.97
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_4",
      "character": "陳懷遠",
      "text": "我明日就要去了，去一個我不知道能不能回來的地方。但在離開之前，我必須讓妳知道：那棟弄堂裡的舊書店，每天下午三點半，當陽光斜照進來的那一刻，我都在想著妳。",
      "voice": "zm_yunxi",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.88
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_5",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "林書瑤認識陳懷遠，是在三年前那個梅雨季節。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_6",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "她去書店躲雨，他正蹲在角落修一盞壞掉的檯燈。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "storytelling",
      "speed": 0.97
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_7",
      "character": "書店老闆",
      "text": "他每星期都來修這盞燈，也每星期都修壞它。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "happy",
      "speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_8",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "後來她才明白，那盞燈從來沒有真正壞過。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_9",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "他們就這樣，用一盞假裝壞掉的燈，撐過了三年的亂世。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.88
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_10",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "然而戰爭從不等人。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "serious",
      "speed": 0.95
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_11",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "一九四九年的冬天，整個城市都在流動。有人南下，有人北上，有人消失在人群裡再也找不到。陳懷遠選擇了一條林書瑤無法跟隨的路。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "serious",
      "speed": 0.95
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_12",
      "character": "陳懷遠",
      "text": "妳不能去。妳還有母親，還有弟弟，還有這座城市需要妳。",
      "voice": "zm_yunxi",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "serious",
      "speed": 0.9
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_13",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "她想反駁，卻發現所有的話都堵在喉嚨裡，像那盞燈——壞掉的樣子，其實是精心偽裝的完整。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.88
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_14",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "他走的那天，她沒有去送他。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.88
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_15",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "不是因為不想，而是因為她知道，如果她去了，她會抓住他的袖子，一輩子不放手。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.85
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_16",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "那樣對他不公平。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_17",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "冬去春來，書店換了老闆，舊燈被換成了新的電燈泡。林書瑤偶爾還是會走進去，在那個角落站一會兒，聽著窗外黃浦江的水聲。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_18",
      "character": "女兒",
      "text": "媽，妳這輩子有沒有後悔過什麼事？",
      "voice": "zf_xiaobei",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "neutral",
      "speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_19",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "林書瑤想了很久。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_20",
      "character": "林書瑤",
      "text": "後悔。有一次，我應該開口說的話，我沒有說。",
      "voice": "zf_xiaobei",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "speed": 0.85
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_21",
      "character": "女兒",
      "text": "那是什麼話？",
      "voice": "zf_xiaobei",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "neutral",
      "speed": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_22",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "她微微笑了。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_23",
      "character": "林書瑤",
      "text": "就是「帶我走」三個字。",
      "voice": "zf_xiaobei",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "whispery",
      "speed": 0.83
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_24",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "窗外，上海的燈火一盞一盞亮起來。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.92
    },
    {
      "id": "seg_25",
      "character": "Narrator",
      "text": "那光，和六十年前弄堂書店裡的燈光，顏色一模一樣。",
      "voice": "zm_yunjian",
      "lang": "zh",
      "emotion": "calm",
      "speed": 0.9
    }
  ]
}
